snippet.title: Without A Crystal Ball
snippet.description:
Without a Crystal Ball is the "fruit Salad" channel of YouTube. Katie Joy covers a variety of topics including reality tv, celebrity gossip, trending news, crime, personal vlogs & More. The channel is most well known for the coverage for Christian Fundamentalism. Many people come here to talk about the Duggars & stay for the variety of topics we cover. 

Interested in sending mail to Without a Crystal Ball? Send it here:

PO Box 120
Hanover, MN 55341


We created a subreddit for followers/fans to share content & interact. The Reddit will post new videos & content we are working on. 

All we ask is for people to be respectful. Trolling, harassment, bullying and hate speech will not be tolerated in the community! 


https://www.reddit.com/r/Woacbofficial/

Follow my social media for the latest updates! 

Twitter: https://twitter.com/katiejoywoacb 

Instagram: https://Instagram.com/withoutacrystalball

Facebook: https://Facebook.com/withoutacrystalball 


Thanks!!

Katie joy
